nodes.text: Moonus Mandel was a planet in the Mid Rim's Bothan sector, and the homeworld of the Veknoid species.
In 58 BBY, during the Mandalorian Civil War, Vizsla planned to conquer Moonus Mandel following the Battle of Concord Dawn. The planet remained neutral during the Clone Wars.
Moonus Mandel was the homeworld of podracer pilot Teemto Pagalies.
